results.name: Decimal expansion of Pi^6/960.
comment: Also the sum of the series Sum_{n>=0} (1/(2n+1)^6), whose value is obtained from zeta(6) given by L. Euler in 1735: Sum_{n>=0}(2n+1)^(-s) = (1-2^(-s))*zeta(s).
results.author: _Iaroslav V. Blagouchine_, Mar 11 2018
